compat-change.description: If an app being installed targets {@link Build.VERSION_CODES#TIRAMISU API 33} and above, the app can be installed without user action. See {@link PackageInstaller.SessionParams#setRequireUserAction} for other conditions required to be satisfied for a silent install.
compat-change.name: SILENT_INSTALL_ALLOWED

compat-change.description: The system supports pre-approval and update ownership features from {@link Build.VERSION_CODES#UPSIDE_DOWN_CAKE API 34}. The change id is used to make sure the system includes the fix of pre-approval with update ownership case. When checking the change id, if it is disabled, it means the build includes the fix. The more detail is on b/293644536. See {@link PackageInstaller.SessionParams#setRequestUpdateOwnership(boolean)} and {@link #requestUserPreapproval(PreapprovalDetails, IntentSender)} for more details.
compat-change.name: PRE_APPROVAL_WITH_UPDATE_OWNERSHIP_FIX

compat-change.description: Throws IllegalArgumentException if the {@link IntentSender} from an immutable {@link android.app.PendingIntent} when caller has a target SDK of API {@link android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES#VANILLA_ICE_CREAM} or above.
compat-change.name: THROW_EXCEPTION_COMMIT_WITH_IMMUTABLE_PENDING_INTENT
